    [Algebra k A] [Algebra k B]
    [Algebra.IsCentral k B] :
    Algebra.IsCentral A (A ‚äó[k] B) := ‚ü®by rw [Algebra.center_baseChange, Algebra.IsCentral.out, Subalgebra.baseChange_bot]‚ü©
```
